00:11:59.830 --> 00:12:03.260
because it's like a mission
for me to convince people.

00:12:03.260 --> 00:12:04.840
So don't worry.

00:12:04.840 --> 00:12:07.810
People can be honest with
me afterwards and tell me

00:12:07.810 --> 00:12:09.800
that they don't like them,
but I'll just commit suicide,

00:12:09.800 --> 00:12:11.930
