00:15:59.180 --> 00:16:02.710
and then with her hands she was
describing the music we were

00:16:02.710 --> 00:16:05.890
playing perfectly.

00:16:05.890 --> 00:16:07.810
You know, it's not about career.

00:16:07.810 --> 00:16:09.110
It's not about anything.

00:16:09.110 --> 00:16:10.410
It's about music.

00:16:10.410 --> 00:16:12.110
&gt;&gt; Nicholas: So if you
