00:17:58.910 --> 00:18:00.210
and there's an inscription inside

00:18:00.210 --> 00:18:03.290
from a famous poet whose
name I always forget.

00:18:03.290 --> 00:18:04.590
It wasn't [inaudible].

00:18:04.590 --> 00:18:07.040
It wasn't [inaudible], and
it wasn't Rufus Wainwright.

00:18:07.040 --> 00:18:09.370
It was somebody.

00:18:09.370 --> 00:18:14.960
[Laughter] One of those
First World War figures,

00:18:14.960 --> 00:18:18.640
and it's this beautiful
little sound.

00:18:18.640 --> 00:18:21.270
A friend of mine, Charles
